itats Directive (92/43/EEC), to protect selected habitats and species.SACs boundaries are mapped using Irish Transverse Mercator (epsg 2157) or Irish Grid (epsg. 29903). Off-shore marine SACs are in WGS84 (epsg 4326) and have their areas calculated in ETRS89 LAEA (epsg 3035). Details of the co-ordinate system for each SAC site can be found in the attribute table of the shapefile.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</idAbs><idPurp>To report on and manage Special Area of Conservation designations within the Republic of Ireland.</idPurp><idCredit>Copyright Government of Ireland. This service was created by National Parks and Wildlife Service, Department of Housing, Local Government and Heritage. This copyright material is licensed for re-use under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International licence.  http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</idCredit><idStatus><ProgCd value="004"/></idStatus><idPoC xmlns=""><rpIndName>NPWS Data Manager</rpIndName><rpOrgName>Department of Housing, Local Government and Heritage</rpOrgName><rpCntInfo xmlns=""><cntAddress addressType="postal"><delPoint>90 North King Street</delPoint><city>Dublin 7</city><postCode>D07 N7CV</postCode><country>IE</country><eMailAdd>datadelivery@housing.gov.ie</eMailAdd></cntAddress></rpCntInfo><role><RoleCd value="007"/></role></idPoC><resMaint xmlns=""><maintFreq><MaintFreqCd value="009"/></maintFreq><maintScp><ScopeCd value="005"/></maintScp><maintCont xmlns=""><rpIndName>NPWS Data Manager</rpIndName><rpOrgName>Department of Housing, Local Government and Heritage</rpOrgName><rpCntInfo xmlns=""><cntAddress addressType="postal"><delPoint>90 North King Street</delPoint><city>Dublin 7</city><postCode> D07 N7CV</postCode><country>IE</country><eMailAdd>datadelivery@housing.gov.ie.ie</eMailAdd></cntAddress></rpCntInfo><role><RoleCd value="007"/></role></maintCont></resMaint><dsFormat xmlns=""><formatName>Esri shapefile</formatName><formatVer>v10.x</formatVer></dsFormat><placeKeys x